 May Friday 25 1917 Came an aw "gutser " today ! Just as we finish up at 10.30 a.m. Sergt . come along say I have to report at Officer ? Mess . D--- B---. Went straight way to W.O. barney with him but no go . Then saw Order Officer promis to do what he could fail . Now behold me waiter in Officer Mess . Ye God The way of the Armi are past find out . Spill the soup drop the spoon , upset the tea , do anyth now till I get out off this job , no good to this chick : Went down to Wimereux in afternoon had tunic fit .
